{"tid":1141033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［政治笑話］北京賓館於昨夜有數十人跳樓自殺","createTime":"2019-05-06T08:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T09:30:24.000Z","uid":19408,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"679c4920c14405eed236075438509b4e99cded2e","tid":1141033,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"某北京賓館於昨夜有數十人跳樓自殺，甚至還有一人猝死於房中，被懷疑鬧鬼。<br />\n後來翻看監控，有個人喝醉了到處敲賓館門，邊敲邊喊：「開門！我是繼偉」。<br />\n幾分鐘後，那人開始上樓，一邊上一邊喊。這時，不斷有人跳下樓去。<br />\n幾分鐘後，他繼續敲門喊的時候，門內有個人冷靜的應了「你是哪裡的紀委，省的還是市的？」<br />\n那人回答：「什麼省的，市的，我是鐘繼偉啊」。<br />\n後來沒人應聲了，等到消防員撬開門的時候發現，原來那人猝死了。"},{"pid":"c52ea18090010fdfedf4dacc4c385e46a46a4068","tid":1141033,"uid":161125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98537dcc32ea0eed76dd1739fe566cb915cf1844","tid":1141033,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8800b22b72f0340bc0f7465b461cb683e21c1862","tid":1141033,"uid":231523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"Link ？"},{"pid":"45981d54cacb8a55299c8b34e016ed40742781c4","tid":1141033,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a349932fa8f7304add8b240230563964cbc81aa9","tid":1141033,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:36:23.000Z","msg":"中紀委恐怖d，定引導條例恐怖d??"},{"pid":"cf1a62d93073e452b206d3e3dc2eaa7ab88b862c","tid":1141033,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif